PRS SE Custom 24 Limited Solidbody Electric Guitar / Case - Matteo Blue -1 of 21 - 7.6 lbs - S/N: R17054 Excellent Condition, 1 of 21 Exclusive These guitars were made exclusively for Spotlight Music in Colorado. Only 21 pieces in this color with Ebony Fretboard, Burled Ash Top, Fretboard Binding, and Burled Ash Headstock were produced. With binding on the headstock, neck, body, these features are unique to the PRS SE Custom 24 line and were only available to the aforementioned music store. This SE Custom 24 features a Burled Ash top, Mahogany back, wide thin Maple neck, Ebony fretboard with bird inlays, and a MannMade vibrato bridge. Its versatile sounds come from the owner installed, aftermarket Seymour Duncan pickups paired with a volume, push/pull tone control, and 3-way blade pickup selector. This gorgeous and exotic looking guitar has been taken care of like a child but actually played. They only made 21 of this special limited run...a rare guitar numbers wise. We're not 100% sure if the case is original to this guitar but it does look like a Gator GWE hard case made exclusively for the SE line. The original 85/15 S pickups were replaced with Seymour Duncan JB/Jazz pups and they are included.
